# ESP32 HX8347 Display Driver

This project provides a draft of an example and driver for interfacing the HX8347 display controller with an ESP32 microcontroller.

## Features

- just a draft. It is not recomended to be used yet

## Requirements

- ESP32s3 development board
- HX8347-based display module

